ment of commercial towers, schools, and hospitals. Buildings will now be permitted to extend to any height, provided they meet advanced firefighting system standards as per NBCS 2026.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/rajasthan-embraces-skyscrapers-new-building-height-regulations-lift-limitations/131475497?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-29210/131475497.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}